title: Extends the biofuel credit and requires all municipalities to use biofuels for any purpose which requires the use of fuel
summary: Extends the biofuel credit and requires all municipalities to use biofuels for any purpose which requires the use of fuel.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the tax law, in relation to extending the biofuel credit and to amend the general municipal law, in relation to requiring all municipalities to use biofuels for any purpose which requires the use of fuel
